data.description: (Seller will NOT entertain "sub-to" or creative financing offers - please no calls on these). Sitting on almost a 1/4 acre homesite with no HOA on Boise's Central Bench - this home is move in ready, with lovely modern updates & original charm! Large windows allow ample natural light to flood in, helping the space feel bright & welcoming! Beautiful refinished hardwood floors, updated plumbing & electrical, granite countertops throughout. Option for Master on main or lower level. French doors take you from the living spaces out back to a serene covered patio. Designated garden space allows you to grow your own food or flowers. Yard is fully fenced, with RV parking behind both fences. Oversized 18x32 single car garage w/multiple 220 plugs + an engine hoist - perfect for those who love to work on cars or simply need extra storage space. Close to BSU, play a round at the Hillcrest Golf Course, play at Ann Morrison or Kathryn Albertsons park, head downtown for dinner, a show, shopping & breweries.
